    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "This (Masculine & Feminine): هذا / هذه",
          "arabic": "هذا / هذه"
        },
        "text": "These are demonstrative pronouns for 'this'. 'هذا' (hādhā) is used for masculine nouns, while 'هذهِ' (hādhihi) is used for feminine nouns. It's important to match the gender.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "هذا كِتاب.",
            "english": "This is a book (m).",
            "transliteration": "Hādhā kitāb."
          },
          {
            "arabic": "هذهِ سيارة.",
            "english": "This is a car (f).",
            "transliteration": "Hādhihi sayyārah."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "That (Masculine & Feminine): ذلك / تلك",
          "arabic": "ذلك / تلك"
        },
        "text": "Similar to 'this', 'that' also has masculine and feminine forms. 'ذلكَ' (dhālika) is for masculine nouns, and 'تلكَ' (tilka) is for feminine nouns.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "ذلكَ بيت.",
            "english": "That is a house (m).",
            "transliteration": "Dhālika bayt."
          },
          {
            "arabic": "تلكَ شجرة.",
            "english": "That is a tree (f).",
            "transliteration": "Tilka shajarah."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Asking for a Specific Price: كم سعر هذا؟",
          "arabic": "كم سعر هذا؟"
        },
        "text": "To ask the price of a specific item, you combine 'كم سعر' (how much price) with the appropriate demonstrative pronoun ('هذا' for masculine, 'هذهِ' for feminine) or the name of the item.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "كم سعرُ هذا القميص؟",
            "english": "How much is this shirt (m)?",
            "transliteration": "Kam si'ru hādhā al-qamīṣ?"
          },
          {
            "arabic": "كم سعرُ تلكَ الساعة؟",
            "english": "How much is that watch (f)?",
            "transliteration": "Kam si'ru tilka as-sā'ah?"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "practice-sentence",
      "sentence": {
        "arabic": "كم سعرُ هذا الهاتف؟",
        "english": "How much is this phone (m)?",
        "transliteration": "Kam si'ru hādhā al-hātif?"
      },
      "context": "Asking the price of a masculine item like a phone."
    },
    {
      "type": "practice-sentence",
      "sentence": {
        "arabic": "أريدُ تلكَ الحقيبة.",
